.TH plfs_chmod 3 "${PACKAGE_STRING}" 
.SH NAME
plfs_chmod 
.SH SYNTAX
#include <plfs.h>
.PP
int plfs_chmod( const char *path, mode_t mode );

.SH DESCRIPTION
Change permissions of a PLFS file.  See chmod(2) for more details.

.SH INPUT PARAMETERS
.TP 1i
path
Path of file to change permissions.
.TP 1i
mode
Permissions to change the file to.

.SH RETURN VALUES
Most PLFS functions return 0 or -errno, except write and read
which return the number of bytes or -errno

